PrecisRevocation of Order in Council P.C. 1984-2293; and revocation of paragraph (a) of Order in Council P.C. 1987-1155 respecting the designation of the Minister of Industry, Science and Technology, subject to paragraphs (b) and (c) of Order in Council P.C. 1987-1155, as the Minister for the purposes of the Industrial and Regional Development Act in relation to any class of matters to which that Act extends in any province or region of a province.
RegistrationRegistration: SI / 1990-0036 Publication Date: 1990-03-14
Attachments
precis:
Revocation of Order in Council P.C. 1984-2293; and revocation of
paragraph (a) of Order in Council P.C. 1987-1155 respecting the
designation of the Minister of Industry, Science and Technology, subject
to paragraphs (b) and (c) of Order in Council P.C. 1987-1155, as the
Minister for the purposes of the Industrial and Regional Development Act
in relation to any class of matters to which that Act extends in any
province or region of a province.
